00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:27,300
That's where the mind comes first.

355
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:28,300
The image comes first.

356
00:16:28,300 --> 00:16:30,300
So primary image.

357
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:32,300
You're thinking there's a side of this image

