00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:33,300
that isn't yours?

359
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:34,300
There's another image.

360
00:16:34,300 --> 00:16:35,300
Within this image.

361
00:16:35,300 --> 00:16:37,300
That image is what experiences are.

362
00:16:37,300 --> 00:16:38,300
Sorry?

