00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:40,300
Yeah.

365
00:16:40,300 --> 00:16:41,300
Of course.

366
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,300
That's what the image looks like.

367
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:43,300
Experience as a whole.

