00:19:15,300 --> 00:19:16,300
in regard to this,

437
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:20,300
which is absence of that image?

438
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:22,300
Think about the empty room.

439
00:19:22,300 --> 00:19:25,300
Yeah, well, yeah.

