00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:55,300
So it's a negative presence,

550
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:59,300
or presence of the absence of certain things.

551
00:23:59,300 --> 00:24:01,300
Dwell on that image.

552
00:24:01,300 --> 00:24:03,300
Presence of absence, basically.

553
00:24:03,300 --> 00:24:06,300
It's not a contradiction because absence...

554
00:24:06,300 --> 00:24:07,300
Is a thing.

